snippet.title: Escape The Pacific - Island Clusters
snippet.description:
This is demo of our island cluster system in Lost In Pacific game. Here are displayed at once only 5 clusters because of engine capability. In the final game there will be displayed only one at a time and their number will be unlimited.

For more information see: https://gamers4gamersteam.com/lost-in-pacific/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/G4GTeam
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Gamers4GamersTeam
IndieDB: http://www.indiedb.com/games/lost-in-pacific

We will upload more videos soon.
